{"tw": {"3427220": {"success": true, "data": {"type": "game", "name": "機械少女琪塔", "steam_appid": 3427220, "required_age": 0, "is_free": false, "detailed_description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3427220/extras/1e06581317e5877fbc24f750997ce8a4.avif?t=1774514373\" width=616 height=73 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3427220/extras/9661589dc81f560ca929af260ff92f8e.poster.avif?t=1774514373\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3427220/extras/9661589dc81f560ca929af260ff92f8e.webm?t=1774514373\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3427220/extras/9661589dc81f560ca929af260ff92f8e.mp4?t=1774514373\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >名為琪塔的少女失去記憶，醒來後發現自己被安置於巨大的機器人內。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >莫名其妙成為叛徒，還遭到追捕的琪塔迫降在一座未開發的島嶼。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >島上到處都是危險的生物、原住民以及追兵，他們全都衝著琪塔而來！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >為何自己會遭遇如此橫禍？隱藏於這座島的秘密和陰謀，正等著少女揭發。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >究竟琪塔是否能安全逃出這座島呢？他的命運，掌握在玩家手上⋯⋯</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3427220/extras/915777da1ca0c2c3cf1e4b7321a6962d.avif?t=1774514373\" width=616 height=73 /></span><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3427220/extras/b03b37ef97c1436f701742e6babca09e.avif?t=1774514373\" width=616 height=275 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>■琪塔（cv.冬沙凪。）</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本遊戲的主角。過去是位大名鼎鼎的天才少女，然而現在卻失去了記憶。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >就在琪塔被當成叛徒追捕時，他不得不迫降在一座未開發的島嶼。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >琪塔個性開朗，面對逆境也不輕言放棄，然而這是否是他原本的個性，則不得而知。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>■莉娜（cv.手塚りょうこ）</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >追捕琪塔的部隊的隊長。個性直率，時常令身邊的人感到困擾。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >過去似乎和琪塔關係深厚，但琪塔並不記得。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><strong>■拉比特</strong></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >琪塔乘坐的機器人——MK-L的輔助AI。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >為失去記憶的琪塔提供許多資訊。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3427220/extras/4f77c6a4b449fe2b5666a9e316ee8b95.avif?t=1774514373\" width=616 height=73 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3427220/extras/faa91e64c9e32d8be9530adac6bfa9a2.poster.avif?t=1774514373\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3427220/extras/faa91e64c9e32d8be9530adac6bfa9a2.webm?t=1774514373\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3427220/extras/faa91e64c9e32d8be9530adac6bfa9a2.mp4?t=1774514373\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >敵人發情了！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >大家都盯上了琪塔！如果無法在戰鬥時打倒敵人，琪塔就會陷入險境！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >華麗的視覺表現！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >結合了3DCG和LIVE2D、精心製作的動畫！身體各個部位都能搖晃、抖動！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >進行探險就能提升等級！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用技能點數進行強化！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >戰鬥贏得勝利時，即可獲得新的戰鬥物品配方！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >提升熟練度就能解鎖更強大的物品！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >武器引擎會隨機升級！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >善加使用武器，讓武器達到理想的狀態！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >以SRPG風格呈現乘著機器人作戰的戰鬥畫面！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >使用收集到的能源改造機體，擊潰追捕琪塔的敵軍！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >各個項目皆有ON／OFF功能，可自由調整難易度！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >玩家可自由選擇遊玩方式，可輕鬆觀看劇情，也能進行高難度的探索和戰鬥！</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3427220/extras/253e9e7226813613b509ac6d4c841bc4.poster.avif?t=1774514373\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3427220/extras/253e9e7226813613b509ac6d4c841bc4.webm?t=1774514373\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3427220/extras/253e9e7226813613b509ac6d4c841bc4.mp4?t=1774514373\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3427220/extras/c96a29a5b09ed2af317e042b7495b0d4.avif?t=1774514373\" width=616 height=73 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3427220/extras/064907379e03b342c9f76e30fa2f9a29.poster.avif?t=1774514373\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3427220/extras/064907379e03b342c9f76e30fa2f9a29.webm?t=1774514373\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3427220/extras/064907379e03b342c9f76e30fa2f9a29.mp4?t=1774514373\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3427220/extras/266ede91ef633421e20d5cce5933145c.poster.avif?t=1774514373\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3427220/extras/266ede91ef633421e20d5cce5933145c.webm?t=1774514373\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3427220/extras/266ede91ef633421e20d5cce5933145c.mp4?t=1774514373\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3427220/extras/6e60eb374cb1ea475c894de207733bc0.poster.avif?t=1774514373\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3427220/extras/6e60eb374cb1ea475c894de207733bc0.webm?t=1774514373\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3427220/extras/6e60eb374cb1ea475c894de207733bc0.mp4?t=1774514373\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span>💠💠【購買前的注意事項】</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >本遊戲使用名為RPGDeveloperBakin的工具製作。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >操作環境預設為RPGDeveloperBakin的建議環境。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >建議可先遊玩試玩版，確認遊戲可正常運作後再購買。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >※AMD生產的CPU(Ryzen)和GPU(Radeon)即使符合建議環境，但仍會產生動畫等部分圖片無法正常顯示等問題。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>", "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3427220/extras/1e06581317e5877fbc24f750997ce8a4.avif?t=1774514373\" width=616 height=73 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3427220/extras/9661589dc81f560ca929af260ff92f8e.poster.avif?t=1774514373\" width=800 height=450 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3427220/extras/9661589dc81f560ca929af260ff92f8e.webm?t=1774514373\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.c